  {
    "id": "f_csv_a6569d32aa",
    "slug": "priced-to-sell-just-the-phrase-makes-me-smile-when-a-dealer-says-all-the-it",
    "texto": "'Priced to sell' - just the phrase makes me smile. When a dealer says all the items in his booth are priced to sell, he means he's tagged them as aggressively as he can to get you to buy them. Don't worry, though, I still haggle. You have to. That's the point of a flea market.",
